name: A lot of Junk & Fruits
description:
JUNKFRUIT!

Whait... what? 

The goal of the game is to eat a lot of good stuff - the fruit! And avoid a lot of bad stuff - the junk! To get rid of the junk, just bubble it up with your bubblenator. But don't bubble up precious fruit...

Assets:

  • UI, Sounds, Fonts, Icons
  • Background Music
  • Junk & Fruits
  • Bubbles
  • Background
  • Env & Player
  • UI Background

Feel free to visit our repo aswell! https://github.com/Nimmda/QuarantineJam
